== Summary ==
Alt text: A graphic announcing VRChat's Developer Update for 29 July 2022. "Now in Live Beta: First Batch of Accessibility & Quality-of-Life Features". On the right side of the graphic is a bullet-point list of features added to the beta. Horizon Adjust, Movable Main Menu, Inverted Look-to-Move Improvement, Personal Mirror, Calibration Mirror, Portal Prompts, Gesture Indactor, Home Instance Types, Particle Limiter Checkbox, Camera/Screenshot Lag Fix, Auto-Disable Avatar Cloning on World Entry, User Notes (On Website)

Source: https://ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-29-july-2022
